					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The N106 allows for both CHR ROM and CHR RAM. One can select 4k CHR banks, and 2 of those 4k pages are CHR RAM. Though I recently read that this mapper is nearly impossible to make a dev cartridge out of, because all of the chips are glob-tops.</div>

					
